Template-Plugin-Digest-SHA2
===========================

The Digest.SHA2 Template Toolkit plugin provides access to the SHA2 algorithm 
via the Digest::SHA2 module.  It is used like a plugin but installs filters 
and vmethods into the current context.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these modules:

  Digest::SHA2
  Template
  Template::Plugin
  Template::Stash

For testing the module requires these modules:

  IO::File
  Test::More

For optional testing the module would like these modules:

  Test::CPAN::Meta
  Test::CPAN::Meta::JSON
  Test::Pod
  Test::Pod::Coverage

